milestones.description: Ranatunga and de Silva's 143-run partnership is SL's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 139 between Ranatunga and de Silva
This is the lowest match aggregate (401) involving teams Sri Lanka & Zimbabwe in ODIs
Sri Lanka's 192-run win against Zimbabwe is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 117-run win against India
